    "en": {
      "title": "Suspect arrested for possession of fuel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A suspect has been arrested by the Special Task Force (STF) in Manipay, Jaffna for storing 630 liters of fuel without a license.",
        "The raid was carried out last night (24) on a tip off received by the STF Jaffna camp that fuel had been stored illegally at the suspect's house.",
        "The arrested suspect is a 27 year old youth who has been handed over to the Manipay Police for further investigations"
      ],
